C. Access Control Systems
Robust access control mechanisms provide essential security boundaries for LLM deployments [20]. This includes tokenbased authentication, session management, and API security measures. These defense mechanisms provide a foundation for securing LLM deployments, but they must be combined with advanced techniques for comprehensive protection. The following section introduces our novel multi-layer defense framework that builds upon these fundamental approaches while adding dynamic trust evaluation and adaptive response capabilities.
